snippet.title: PUBG - Patch Report - Update 8.1
snippet.description:
The Jungle Calls. Season 8 brings you a remastered Sanhok with new and updated locations, features, and tools. The postponed Gas Can improvements from Season 7 are also back! Check out our latest Patch Report or read the full patch notes for more details!
